<h3>Creating an Options Object</h3>

As everyone, including, myself are complaining about the complexity of the API, we are going to try and create an options object, in order to see if we can simplify it.

Our aim is to be able to call the progress bar as follows:

{{plain:
progressBar(options);
}}

The options we need to set, other than the css, it should be set-up on the page are as follows:

{{plain:

   interval: microseconds    // timer interval
   step     : delta              // step
   hide     : true                // hides
}}



